<h2 id="state-words">State and Texture Words (擬態語 Gitaigo)</h2>

<p>These describe how things look, feel, or exist — even though they don't make actual sounds. Usually written in hiragana or katakana.</p>

<table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin:1.5rem 0;">
  <thead>
